Name: Total duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities in cases where 'Completed + In Call' also occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before transitioning to any 'Accepted + In Progress' activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Longest duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' without transitioning to another activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' leading to a 'Completed + Resolved' state
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities across all cases in the log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to the next activity in cases ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Duration variability of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' across different organization countries
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Earliest occurrence of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in relation to 'Completed + In Call' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Latest occurrence of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before any 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases with more than one occurrence of this activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case where activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched occurs

Name: Comparison of average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases with and without 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Total elapsed time of all 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities before reaching 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average lead time to 'Completed + In Call' from the first occurrence of 'Unmatched + Unmatched'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Median duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in comparison to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'
